parameters:
\SE[92]It's frightening how smoothly I was able to
infiltrate....

\SE[10]But, from now on, it's the maid interview!
\SE[10]This is where the real deal begins...!

\SE[12]I've investigated Lord Donyoku's preferences in
women! \SE[12]He likes women who are neat, graceful, and
pure and virtuous...! \SE[10]In other words, me and my
sister are a perfect match!!

No, no, where do we have the elements of being neat,
graceful, and pure and virtuous?

\SE[55]I'm skilled at wearing the cat disguise...!
\SE[55]In other words, as long as my sister can fully play
the role, there won't be any problems at all!

\SE[20]Kuh...! Don't suddenly pull the ladder out from under
me...! \SE[68]Role-playing... Role-playing... Right.

\SE[2]No, I think it'll work out just fine! After all,
you're also a well-bred young lady! \SE[0]...As long as we
can suppress the violent tendencies.

\SE[0]I apologize for the wait. It is Vega-sama and Cat-
sama who wish for the maid interview, correct? \SE[0]Please
allow me to guide you to the master's bedroom.

\SE[12] (...I see. \SE[3] The person Laura-san and the
others were talking about, Nikita...)

\SE[3] (It seems like contact will be easy. The start is
promising.)
\SE[2]Um... Is there something on my face...?
